== 0.1.8 - 20-Nov-2015
* This gem is now signed.
* Gem related tasks in the Rakefile now assume Rubygems 2.x.
* Updated gemspec, removing rubyforge_project and adding cert_chain.
* Added a win32-sapi.rb file for convenience.

== 0.1.7 - 23-Aug-2013
* Removed windows-pr as a development dependency. Added rake and
  test-unit as development dependencies.
* Updates to the README and gemspec files.
* Updated gem:create task for Rubygems 2.x.

== 0.1.6 - 17-Jan-2011
* Some Rakefile and gemspec updates.
* Two tests now skipped on Windows XP.
* Added windows-pr as a development dependency.

== 0.1.5 - 10-Aug-2009
* Changed license to Artistic 2.0.
* Some gemspec updates, including license and description.
* Changed test and example file names.
* Added some class level comments within the source file.

== 0.1.4 - 29-Jul-2007
* Added a Rakefile with tasks for installation and testing.
* Removed the install.rb file. The Rakefile now handles installation.
* Removed the doc/sapi5.txt file. It was merged into the README.
* Some doc updates.

== 0.1.3 - 9-Nov-2005
* Fixed SpInProcRecognizer class name.

== 0.1.2 - 17-Jun-2005
* Added a gemspec.
* Some minor updates to the README and test file.
* Removed the doc/sapi5.rd file.  Made the doc/sapi5.txt file roc friendly.

== 0.1.1 - 1-Mar-2005
* Moved the 'examples' directory to the toplevel directory.
* Made the CHANGES and README files rdoc friendly.

== 0.1.0 - 12-Oct-2004
* Initial release
